subject: J2EEUnit 0.5 now available
msgSnippet: J2EEUnit version 0.5 is now available for download on http://j2eeunit.sourceforge.net J2EEUnit is a testing framework based on JUnit for unit testing
messageBody:
J2EEUnit version 0.5 is now available for download on
http://j2eeunit.sourceforge.net

J2EEUnit is a testing framework based on JUnit for unit testing
server-side java code (Servlets, JSP, ...).

For a list of the features, see :
http://j2eeunit.sourceforge.net/technical/features.html

For the changelog between version 0.4 and this new 0.5 version ,
see : http://sourceforge.net/project/shownotes.php?
group_id=14156&release_id=19473

Thanks.
Vincent.
